WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.110

2
00:00:00.110 --> 00:00:03.750
Hello, my name is On.

3
00:00:03.750 --> 00:00:04.710
I'm from Thailand.

4
00:00:04.710 --> 00:00:06.390
My question is:

5
00:00:06.390 --> 00:00:07.980
would I rather

6
00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:10.100
write a paper or take a test?

7
00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:12.040
My answer is: I would rather

8
00:00:12.040 --> 00:00:14.440
write a paper just because

9
00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:19.000
I do not like the stress that I get

10
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.530
in the short period of time

11
00:00:21.530 --> 00:00:22.880
when I take a test.

12
00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:25.180
Moreover, if I write a paper

13
00:00:25.180 --> 00:00:28.210
I have more time to do research,

14
00:00:28.210 --> 00:00:29.820
what I do not understand,

15
00:00:29.820 --> 00:00:32.150
and I can manage my own schedule

16
00:00:32.150 --> 00:00:33.610
of when I want to do it.

17
00:00:33.610 --> 00:00:35.100
Therefore, that I can finish

18
00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:38.047
to the deadline.

